  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil's fate has been fulfilled",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Hareen Fernando said that it was written in his destiny that Ranil Wickramasinghe should be sworn in as President and that is what has happened now.",
        "He said the above while speaking to the media after the election for the President was over."
      ],
